Map Name :- gg_slagg_southerncross

Date Made:- 1st May 2012

Type:- Gun Game

Info:- This is my first CS:S map for deathmatch Gun Games and I hope you will enjoy it



Installation

Place the map into the 'map' directory in the cstrike section e.g.

steam>steamApps>yourusername>counterstrike_source>cstrike>maps

Then open counterstrike and play. It should work.

Thankyou for checking it out :)
